OL,3,CMillions more Brits abroad eligible to
OL,4,Cvote in UK General Election
OL,6,FMillions more Britons who moved abroad
OL,7,Fwill be able to vote in the UK's
OL,8,Fupcoming election following a law
OL,9,Fchange earlier this year.
OL,11,FThe 2024 General Election, announced
OL,12,Fby Rishi Sunak , will be the first to
OL,13,Fallow expats who left the UK more than
OL,14,F15 years ago to vote.
OL,16,FThe UK Government estimate that the
OL,17,Fnumber of expats now eligible to vote
OL,18,Fwill have increased from around one
OL,19,Fmillion to between 3.2 and 3.3 million.
