OL,3,CMillions more Brits abroad eligible to
OL,4,Cvote in UK General Election
OL,6,FCampaign groups like British In Europe
OL,7,Fbelieve the move aligns the UK with
OL,8,Fother major democracies, such as the
OL,9,FUS, Canada, and France, where citizens
OL,10,Fhave a lifelong right to vote.
OL,12,FIn a post on its website, the group
OL,13,Fsays: "Ultimately, voting is not
OL,14,Fcompulsory in the UK, so you don't
OL,15,Fhave to vote if you don't want to, but
OL,16,Fthe new rules mean that those who do
OL,17,Fwant to vote can."
