OL,6,FOnce , Brits living abroad can remain
OL,7,Fregistered for up to three years.
OL,8,FAfter that, they must renew their
OL,9,Fregistration or be removed from the
OL,10,Fregister and have to apply again.
OL,12,FPreviously, an overseas voter could
OL,13,Fonly vote in elections for up to 15
OL,14,Fyears after they left the UK. That
OL,15,Flimit was scrapped in January 2024.
