OL,6,FThat depends on whether the person
OL,7,Fwill be temporarily out of the country
OL,8,Fon election day or have permanently
OL,9,Fmoved overseas.
OL,11,FIn most cases, they can either vote by
OL,12,Fproxy (appointing someone in the UK to
OL,13,Fvote in person on their behalf) or
OL,14,Fvote by post.
